reviews.review_text:
Incredible quality I'm plowing through all '73 shows, and there is a run of summer shows that just don't have crisp recordings. Not that case here! This is absolutely impeccable quality. 

I don't love the horn sit-ins early in the second set, and to be honest lots of the second set is skippable. But I'm here to talk about the quality! Which, again, is first class. Bravo.
